{"id":30,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":30,"title":"Matthew 28","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 28"],[".studySummary",["i","Christ the Lord is risen—He appears to many—He has all power in heaven and earth—He sends the Apostles to teach and baptize all nations."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.1","order":"03.03.028.3934"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"In"],"the end of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"sabbath"],", as it began to dawn toward the first",["i","day"],"of the week, came Mary Magdalene and the other Mary to see the sepulchre."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.2","order":"03.03.028.3935"},["b","2"],"And, behold, there was a great earthquake: for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"the"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"angel"],"of the Lord descended from heaven, and came and rolled back the stone from the door, and sat upon it."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.3","order":"03.03.028.3936"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"His"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"countenance"],"was like lightning, and his raiment white as snow:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.4","order":"03.03.028.3937"},["b","4"],"And for fear of him the keepers did shake, and became as dead",["i","men."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.5","order":"03.03.028.3938"},["b","5"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"And"],"the angel answered and said unto the women, Fear not ye: for I know that ye seek Jesus, which was crucified."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.6","order":"03.03.028.3939"},["b","6"],"He is not here: for he is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"risen"],", as he said. Come, see the place where the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Lord"],"lay."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.7","order":"03.03.028.3940"},["b","7"],"And go quickly, and tell his disciples that he is risen from the dead; and, behold, he goeth before you into Galilee; there shall ye see him: lo, I have told you."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.8","order":"03.03.028.3941"},["b","8"],"And they departed quickly from the sepulchre with fear and great joy; and did run to bring his disciples word."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.9","order":"03.03.028.3942"},["b","9"],"¶And as they went to tell his disciples, behold,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Jesus"],"met them, saying, All hail. And they came and held him by the feet, and worshipped him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.10","order":"03.03.028.3943"},["b","10"],"Then said Jesus unto them, Be not afraid: go tell my brethren that they go into Galilee, and there shall they see me."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.11","order":"03.03.028.3944"},["b","11"],"¶Now when they were going, behold, some of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"watch"],"came into the city, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"shewed"],"unto the chief priests all the things that were done."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.12","order":"03.03.028.3945"},["b","12"],"And when they were assembled with the elders, and had taken counsel, they gave",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"large money"],"unto the soldiers,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.13","order":"03.03.028.3946"},["b","13"],"Saying, Say ye, His disciples came by night, and stole him",["i","away"],"while we slept."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.14","order":"03.03.028.3947"},["b","14"],"And if this come to the governor’s ears, we will persuade him, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"secure you"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.15","order":"03.03.028.3948"},["b","15"],"So they took the money, and did as they were taught: and this saying is commonly reported among the Jews until this day."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.16","order":"03.03.028.3949"},["b","16"],"¶Then the eleven disciples went away into Galilee, into a mountain where Jesus had appointed them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.17","order":"03.03.028.3950"},["b","17"],"And when they saw him, they worshipped him: but some",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"doubted"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18","order":"03.03.028.3951"},["b","18"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Jesus"],"came and spake unto them, saying, All",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"power"],"is given unto me in heaven and in earth."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.19","order":"03.03.028.3952"},["b","19"],"¶Go ye therefore, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"teach"],"all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"nations"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"baptizing"],"them in the name of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"Father"],", and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.20","order":"03.03.028.3953"},["b","20"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Teaching"],"them to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"observe"],"all things whatsoever I have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"commanded"],"you: and, lo,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"I"],"am with you alway,",["i","even"],"unto the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_20e"},"end"],"of the world. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.1a","order":"03.03.028.3954"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"After the sabbath."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.1b","order":"03.03.028.3956"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.2a","order":"03.03.028.3958"},["b","2a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 28:2 …",["i","two angels"],"…"],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.2b","order":"03.03.028.3960"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.3a","order":"03.03.028.3962"},["b","3a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 28:3",["i","And their"],"countenance was like lightning, and",["i","their"],"raiment white as snow …"],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.3b","order":"03.03.028.3964"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.6"},"D&C 20:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.5a","order":"03.03.028.3966"},["b","5a"],["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 28:4 And the",["i","angels"],"answered and said unto the women, Fear not ye; for",["i","we"],"know …"],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.6a","order":"03.03.028.3968"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.6b","order":"03.03.028.3970"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lord"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.9a","order":"03.03.028.3972"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.11a","order":"03.03.028.3974"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"guard."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.11b","order":"03.03.028.3976"},["b","11b"],["span.small","GR"],"reported."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.12a","order":"03.03.028.3978"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"much money."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.14a","order":"03.03.028.3980"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"keep you out of trouble."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.17a","order":"03.03.028.3982"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/doubt"},"TG Doubt"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18a","order":"03.03.028.3984"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.18b","order":"03.03.028.3986"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/2.8"},"Heb. 2:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.6"},"1 Ne. 9:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"Jesus Christ, Messiah"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"Jesus Christ, Power of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.19a","order":"03.03.028.3988"},["b","19a"],["span.small","GR"],"preach to, make disciples of (meaning “make Christians in all nations”).",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"Israel, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"Missionary Work"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-early-saints"},"Mission of Early Saints"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"},"Mission of Latter-day Saints"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching"},"Teaching"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.19b","order":"03.03.028.3990"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/nations"},"TG Nations"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/28.19c","order":"03.03.028.3992"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-essential"},"Baptism, Essential"],"."],["div",{"id":"